data.description: **Seller will pay up to $5,000 towards buyers closing with an acceptable offer.**Welcome to 482 Live Oak. This beautiful home is a must see! This home has tons of upgrades including new marble kitchen countertops, freshly painted kitchen cabinets, new subway tile backsplash, new kitchen hardware, new kitchen faucet with a farmhouse sink.  The great room, dining area and kitchen are open with high specialty ceilings and a gas log fireplace. Kitchen is open and spacious with island. The master suite features specialty ceiling, double vanity, tiled shower, jetted tub and walk-in closet. The master bath has freshly painted cabinets. The laundry room is connected to the master suite. This home features plantation shutters throughout and hardwood flooring throughout the main level. Upstairs is a bonus room and a 4th bedroom and a full bathroom. Fenced in backyard for privacy. Large patio space in the backyard with covered patio. Utility garage in the back as well. Gated subdivision with sidewalks, clubhouse and community pool. Clubhouse is equipped with a workout room accessible by residents. Make your appointment today to view this home.
